  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "PROJECT MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a proactive and organized individual to support our project team under the supervision of the Project Manager.<br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Coordinate with clients and internal teams to ensure smooth project execution.</li><li>Assist in procurement and purchasing of materials as requested by the site team.</li><li>Liaise with suppliers to track deliveries and ensure timely arrival of materials.</li><li>Handle administrative tasks related to the project, including preparation and submission of paperwork.</li><li>Prepare and maintain safety and compliance documents required by the site.</li><li>Coordinate with subcontractors to ensure work is carried out according to schedule and quality standards.</li><li>Support drafting and documentation using AutoCAD (ACAD knowledge is an advantage).</li><li>Assist the project team in daily operations and ad hoc tasks as required.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or degree in Engineering, Construction Management, or related field is preferred.</li><li>Fresh Graduate are welcome Prior experience in construction projects, procurement, or site coordination is an advantage.</li><li>Good organizational and communication skills.</li><li>Proficient in MS Office (Word, Excel, Outlook).</li><li>AutoCAD knowledge is a plus.</li><li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment and manage multiple tasks simultaneously.</li><li>Strong teamwork spirit and willingness to learn.</li></ul>",
