    "uen": "201538584E",
    "description": "<p>Incorporated in Singapore in 2015, Dynamech System specializes in Fire Protection Systems. Such systems include Fire Alarm System, Sprinkler System, Clean Agent System and Foam System in both the public and private sectors. For the past year, Dynamech System has grown progressively to its current strength.</p>\n\n<p>ACMV plays a part in Fire Protection Systems as well. Such systems include Smoke Control System and Smoke Extraction System.</p>\n\n<p>Therefore, there is a need for us to integrate these systems together as a solution for both the client and the owner.</p>\n\n<p>With the commitment and dedication of the top management leading the team, together with the vast experience and expertise of our committed and dedicated key personnel and staff, our goal is to go beyond the needs of engineering and provide solutions for our clients.</p>\n",
